  Jira issue / ID       Request log CSV / sheet          Summary CSV report

config/
scripts/
docs/
sample_data/
logs/
1. Slack user submits request
2. slack_listener.py parses mock_slack_payload.json
3. workflow_controller.py receives RequestEvent
4. workflow_controller.py calls jira_ticket_creator.create_jira_ticket()
5. jira_ticket_creator.py returns ticket key / ID
6. workflow_controller.py calls gworkspace_logger.log_request()
7. gworkspace_logger.py writes a row to request_log.csv
8. workflow_controller.py calls generate_csv_report.build_summary()
9. generate_csv_report.py updates example_csv_report.csv
10. workflow_controller.py logs the full workflow in logs/ppi_activity_log.txt
Slack Request Received
        |
        v
Validate Payload -----> Invalid? -----> Log error and stop
        |
        v
Create Jira Ticket ----> Failure? ----> Log failure and stop
        |
        v
Log to Request Log CSV
        |
        v
Generate / Update Summary CSV
        |
        v
Write Activity Log
        |
        v
Return Success Result

